// Beta points at AWS **dev** — the config used for TestFlight builds, so betas
// exercise the real AWS dev backend (auto-deployed from main) without touching
// prod. Release stays on prod (App Store); Debug stays on localhost.
//
// Same per-install Cognito auth as Release (no dev-user creds) — just the dev
// pool/client, so a TestFlight tester signs in exactly like a real user, against
// the dev user pool. See docs/ios-environments.md.
//
// Dev API (terraform output api_url, envs/dev). The `$()` splits the `//` so
// xcconfig doesn't treat the rest of the line as a comment.
API_BASE_URL = https:/$()/dy9kj15vph.execute-api.us-east-1.amazonaws.com
API_BEARER_TOKEN =
COGNITO_REGION = us-east-1
COGNITO_CLIENT_ID = 7oki1ajf3fh3v6j3avacim3g8f
COGNITO_DEV_USERNAME =
COGNITO_DEV_PASSWORD =
